      "review_summary": "The PR replaces direct successful-response `response.json()` calls in Discord, Feishu, Google Meet, and Tlon plugin paths with `readProviderJsonResponse`, updates nearby tests, and raises plugin SDK surface-report budgets.\n\nPR surface: Source +32, Tests +22, Other 0. Total +54 across 14 files.\n\nReproducibility: yes. at source level: current main still has native successful-response JSON readers in the targeted plugin paths, while the shared helper source shows the bounded 16 MiB failure behavior. I did not run a live external-service OOM reproduction in this read-only review.",
